# Machine-local config overrides (paths, network IPs, USB device paths).
# Schema lives in config_local.example.py (committed).
config_local.py

# Perception model weights (FastSAM-s.pt ~23 MB, depth_pro.pt ~1.9 GB) are
# fetched out of band and never committed. PERCEPTION_MODELS_DIR normally
# points outside the tree, but ignore an in-tree models/ dir defensively.
perception/models/
perception/output/

# Model weights: large weights (FastSAM-s.pt, depth_pro.pt) are never committed
# and resolve from PERCEPTION_MODELS_DIR. The gaze YOLO weight yolo26n.pt IS
# committed at the repo root — gaze_system.py loads it by bare name
# (YOLO("yolo26n.pt") → cwd), so it must travel with the repo. Only the older,
# genuinely-unused yolo11n/yolov8n were meant to be removed in 6054e07;
# yolo26n.pt's untrack there was unintended and is restored via the !/ exception.
*.pt
!/yolo26n.pt

# Calibration pose libraries are machine-local runtime data. The active one
# resolves via config.POSE_LIBRARY_PATH; harmony_calibration_exec.py writes a
# new poses_with_gaze_<stamp>.npz per calibration.
*.npz

# Orphaned online-run output (confusion_matrix_*.csv) used to land here from a
# now-retired writer; the live code logs to text only. Ignore defensively.
/Data/
